    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "@Haroenv no I didn't! \r\nThat does work!\r\n```js\r\nvar search = instantsearch({\r\n      ...\r\n      searchParameters: {\r\n            enableRules: false\r\n      }\r\n});\r\n```\r\n👍 \r\nNow being able to do this without code change, through an `enableRules` query parameter, would be nice. \r\nBut I could implement my own solution to enable/disable this setting though. Since it is part of the `searchParameter`, it makes it easy to do.",
